AutoBot Software License
========================

Copyright (c) 2025-2026 mrveiss. All rights reserved.


PREAMBLE
--------

This software is shared openly and without restriction. You are free to use
it, build with it, modify it, distribute it, and profit from it — no
permission needed, no fees, no gatekeeping.

This project exists because of time, effort, and a genuine desire to build
something useful and share it with the world. If it helps you build something
profitable, we simply ask that you consider giving something back — whether
that's code, financial support, or anything else that helps keep the project
alive and moving forward.

Every contribution, however small, directly supports the continuity of
AutoBot. It funds future development, keeps the project maintained, and
ensures that the Software remains available, improved, and free for everyone.
When you support the project, you are not just giving back — you are helping
guarantee that AutoBot continues to exist and grow for yourself and for
everyone else who depends on it.

There is no mandated amount. There is no enforcement mechanism for honest
people. This is an appeal to fairness, not a legal trap. If you profit from
this software and you choose to contribute something — however small — you
are doing the right thing and it is appreciated.

Everything below is there to make the terms clear and to protect both parties.


